    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the written or printed characters that denote units in a numerical sequence. For the abstract units belonging to a mathematical system and subject to specified laws of succession, addition, and other functions, use "numbers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
